                                We hire extremely talented people from quantitative and engineering disciplines. They do not only
                                have strong quantitative and engineering skills but have demonstrated an ability to solve technical
                                problems and want to constantly learn and grow their skills.
        
                                See the jobs section below for our open positions. If you don't see the position you're looking for
                                we would still love to hear from you. Contact us at <a href="#">info@blytix.com</a>.
                            </p>
                            </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="ion-ios-add icon"></div>    
                        <div class="accordion">Where will I work from?</div>
                        <div class="panel">
